Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.78,0:02:13.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如何?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.34,0:02:15.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如何{\rsymbol}…{\r}什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.22,0:02:23.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我發現 從這裡能望到島上的實驗場
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.81,0:02:26.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想確認要不要封鎖一下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.76,0:02:32.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然看得到鐵塔 但無法直接觀察實驗場
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.04,0:02:34.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,應該不必封鎖
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.20,0:02:36.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,南條特務中尉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.12,0:02:39.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.49,0:02:42.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就這些?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.39,0:02:51.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這地方不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.75,0:02:52.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.05,0:02:56.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為實在太漂亮了 想讓左文字先生也看看
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.21,0:02:57.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.25,0:03:01.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這種地方還有好多 下次再帶你去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.28,0:03:33.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,塵歸塵 土歸土
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.34,0:03:37.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,銀色悲劇要歸為無嗎{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.30,0:03:41.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,立個墓碑又有何不可呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.38,0:03:51.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,將抹不去的恐懼 用喧囂和享樂掩蓋的{\rsymbol}…{\r}虛偽城市
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.23,0:03:58.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人類只有這種時候顯得格外幹練
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.62,0:04:00.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無所謂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.30,0:04:05.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道的人永遠記得就夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.13,0:04:11.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,至少明白你還沒忘 我就安心了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.47,0:04:14.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,始本 託你件事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.44,0:04:15.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.36,0:04:19.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去查查船為什麼晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.43,0:04:21.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得有蹊蹺
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.79,0:04:23.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.85,0:04:24.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有勞了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.80,0:04:31.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.02,0:04:34.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以等你吧 元帥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.33,0:04:37.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在是中尉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.54,0:04:48.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐{\rsymbol}…{\r}曾在這裡呆過
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.69,0:05:12.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,左文字隊長
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.89,0:05:16.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,銀色殲滅者的升級如何了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.28,0:05:21.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,結束後 經鈴城曹長批准
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.63,0:05:23.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帶哈茲福特小姐來了島上
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.21,0:05:24.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.27,0:05:28.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回去路上 偶然間發現了這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.55,0:05:29.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,隊長您呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.01,0:05:33.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,朋友介紹的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.61,0:05:36.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很久前的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.03,0:05:38.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.35,0:05:40.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡景色好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.29,0:05:43.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,進上等兵
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.95,0:05:44.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.19,0:05:48.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谷田他們正在準備接收物資
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.14,0:05:51.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回野營地做搬入準備吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.12,0:05:52.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.63,0:06:11.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有聯絡 卡普少佐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.93,0:06:14.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好 傳令第四大隊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.57,0:06:15.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,準備攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.33,0:06:16.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.90,0:06:20.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,赫魯姆斯中佐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.78,0:06:23.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,里希特霍芬發來聯絡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.86,0:06:25.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已成功潛入
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.21,0:06:26.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.00,0:06:30.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,您覺得這不妥嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.38,0:06:32.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當然了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.31,0:06:34.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個白癡准將
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.34,0:06:38.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,居然借里希特霍芬去參與這種行動{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.85,0:06:40.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,盡做些無聊事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.50,0:06:46.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,配合前方的總攻擊 從背後奇襲擾敵{\rsymbol}…{\r}嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.07,0:06:49.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖說最近確實進軍緩慢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.35,0:06:51.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這招也真夠大膽
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.61,0:06:54.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是{\rsymbol}…{\r}下下簽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.57,0:06:57.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,既然抽到 就要做好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.33,0:07:15.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能出發了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.69,0:07:17.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的 就快了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.43,0:07:19.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是幹什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.80,0:07:23.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 你想光著屁股在城裡衝嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.58,0:07:25.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大哥 你可饒了我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.62,0:07:28.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,任務中別沒大沒小的 托馬斯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.67,0:07:30.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,失敬了 托格爾斯軍曹
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.93,0:07:34.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,伍長說得沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.36,0:07:35.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是偽裝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.41,0:07:40.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,關卡的工作人員已經買通 不必擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.30,0:07:43.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,城裡有阿蘭達斯的軍人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.11,0:07:48.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小規模的獨立部隊為做補給在附近野營了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.59,0:07:51.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 他們壞不了事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.18,0:07:54.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,儘快給我弄完
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.10,0:08:06.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎回來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.46,0:08:06.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有情況嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.43,0:08:09.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有 很順利
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.72,0:08:10.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谷田他們呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.39,0:08:14.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接到補給 正往這邊趕
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.47,0:08:15.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,估計快到了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.74,0:08:17.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.19,0:08:20.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回來之後抓緊裝貨
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.64,0:08:21.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.58,0:08:26.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,始本先生來聯絡過
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.26,0:08:31.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說什麼了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.93,0:08:33.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,倒沒什麼值得注意的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.99,0:08:36.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們見面了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.38,0:08:37.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.35,0:08:39.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,闊別多年啊{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.22,0:08:40.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是呢{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.11,0:08:45.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一直挺擔心他離開軍隊後過得怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.30,0:08:47.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看來依舊硬朗啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.58,0:08:49.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.65,0:08:50.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他依舊那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.39,0:08:59.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要確認敵人動向
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.33,0:09:01.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去聯絡大隊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.36,0:09:03.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.75,0:09:19.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐 為什麼在這
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.87,0:09:23.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,呐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.39,0:09:25.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大夥都回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.05,0:09:27.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊{\rsymbol}…{\r}哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.55,0:09:29.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.03,0:09:44.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,呐 療養溫泉如何
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.59,0:09:45.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.72,0:09:47.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全都拿回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.80,0:09:48.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.08,0:09:51.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,隨後我們要向格維茨平原轉移
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.37,0:09:56.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,前線有動作 可能很快會發起總攻
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.13,0:09:57.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.59,0:09:59.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好嘞 快點了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.11,0:10:00.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.94,0:10:22.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因戈爾米亞要裝貨?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.94,0:10:23.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.76,0:10:26.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這就是那條船晚點的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.00,0:10:28.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,至於貨物清單
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.37,0:10:30.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是工業機械配件
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.24,0:10:35.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卸貨之後放在附近工廠了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.56,0:10:39.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這工廠的擁有者叫戈爾吉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.31,0:10:42.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是這有名的因戈爾米亞擁護者
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.41,0:10:44.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.65,0:10:46.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後才是有趣的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.90,0:10:52.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,戈爾吉的工廠有三台工業用機械 已經向上面申請出貨
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.91,0:10:55.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,通關時間 預計是今晚20點
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.31,0:10:59.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,寺井
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.93,0:11:00.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.20,0:11:02.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,叫席加行動
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.86,0:11:03.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.64,0:11:06.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下次見面再道謝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.67,0:11:08.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別讓我把頭髮等白了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.92,0:11:09.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不保證
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.93,0:11:11.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,席加先生出動了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.93,0:11:38.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,搞定了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.20,0:11:40.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊{\rsymbol}…{\r}哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.19,0:11:46.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要緊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.54,0:11:47.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誒?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.53,0:11:48.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.63,0:11:53.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽好 注意力集中點
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.64,0:12:03.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,思維脈衝驅動裝置 GO
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.91,0:12:04.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,傳感陣列 啟動
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.40,0:12:07.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,確認環境信息統合
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.48,0:12:08.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,兵裝擴展 激活
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.45,0:12:11.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,銀色殲滅者 全系統啟動
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.52,0:12:20.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也對
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.89,0:12:21.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在不行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.42,0:12:24.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不能光琢磨姐姐那件事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.89,0:12:50.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到了這 就只等著踢那群混蛋的屁股了吧 大哥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.18,0:12:52.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,閉嘴 托馬斯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.51,0:12:53.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒事少瞎通信
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.94,0:13:19.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,趕上了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.12,0:13:21.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.88,0:13:56.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,曳戰者!?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.99,0:13:58.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那部新型機嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.54,0:13:59.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,居然在這
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.37,0:14:06.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,時宗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.29,0:14:08.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就阻截這一點上值得表揚
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.98,0:14:13.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是說其他都夠嗆哦 時宗君
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.80,0:14:14.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.20,0:14:18.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,通知總部 總攻時間後移
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.79,0:14:22.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等我們清除障礙後 再繼續計劃
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.19,0:14:29.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不會讓你礙事 新型機
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.14,0:14:41.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,少尉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.21,0:14:43.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總部決定終止計劃
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.16,0:14:45.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓我們立刻撤離
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.84,0:14:47.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,計劃還可以繼續
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.80,0:14:49.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,給我告訴總部
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.01,0:14:59.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此 動作變快了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.71,0:15:04.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是 上升的不是機師水準 而是機體反應性能
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.44,0:15:14.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.26,0:15:17.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阻止奇襲的目的已經達成
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.25,0:15:19.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不必過分追擊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.43,0:15:29.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是沒想追 可對面{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.08,0:15:35.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大哥 不是撤退嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.77,0:15:37.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不能丟下少尉不管
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.93,0:15:39.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,各位請看
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.99,0:15:43.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在緩衝地帶貝爾哈羅斯的海岸 此刻正發生戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.15,0:15:46.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,海岸雖然不是非戰鬥區
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.33,0:15:49.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但不知損害何時會波及貝爾哈羅斯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.39,0:15:53.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣下去 美麗的貝爾哈羅斯市也會成為戰場嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.68,0:15:55.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不會讓這種事發生的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.71,0:15:56.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有我家元帥在
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.53,0:15:59.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把赤影派到能看見橋的位置
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.46,0:16:02.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,出現萬一就把橋炸掉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.96,0:16:03.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.19,0:16:19.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟丟了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.49,0:16:23.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吃我一招
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.77,0:16:38.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,贏了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.74,0:16:47.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,勞倫斯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.56,0:16:48.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好嘞
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.04,0:16:56.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,托馬斯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.57,0:17:06.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,疼疼疼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.13,0:17:07.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.81,0:17:14.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,糟{\rsymbol}…{\r}糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.34,0:17:17.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋們 居然把托馬斯{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.61,0:17:23.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘁
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.36,0:17:24.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.15,0:17:51.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,時宗機 被壓制中
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.96,0:17:53.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希爾菲 前去支援
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.72,0:17:54.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,了解了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.56,0:18:15.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你到此為止了 新型機
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.79,0:18:18.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.16,0:18:34.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.35,0:18:42.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拼了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.98,0:18:45.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,少尉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.89,0:18:54.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,托格爾斯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.77,0:18:56.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,少尉 請快撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.41,0:18:57.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.00,0:18:58.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,少尉!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.93,0:19:19.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.83,0:19:25.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新型機{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.27,0:19:28.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有里希特霍芬一人 成功撤離
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.25,0:19:30.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去回收
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.24,0:19:33.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我稍微{\rsymbol}…{\r}冷靜一下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.95,0:19:47.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,格維茨平原上敵人已停止動作
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.79,0:19:49.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,戰況沒有變化
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.20,0:19:52.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因意外情況計劃緊急中止
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.03,0:19:53.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,估計不會錯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.12,0:19:56.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們就是那個{\rsymbol2}「{\r}意外情況{\rsymbol2}」{\r}呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.04,0:20:18.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,時宗的直覺果然對了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.73,0:20:21.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不是說他們也是軍人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.03,0:20:24.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,居然是因戈爾米亞軍
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.00,0:20:28.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.94,0:20:29.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誒
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.62,0:20:30.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊{\rsymbol}…{\r}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.07,0:20:31.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.97,0:20:34.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,挺厲害嘛 聯動深度17
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.03,0:20:35.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.12,0:20:38.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,與銀色殲滅者連接的深度
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.14,0:20:40.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我沒說過嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.75,0:20:43.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,話說這個 等於考試17分吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.60,0:20:44.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,厲害嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.84,0:20:47.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剛開了幾星期 已經不錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.69,0:20:49.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不覺得比之前靈活了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.23,0:20:51.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 好像是有
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.22,0:20:53.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不如說今天才第一次{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.82,0:20:55.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.21,0:20:59.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,覺得真正戰鬥過了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.58,0:21:01.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,唔?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.38,0:21:09.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都毀了啊 吉米喜歡的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.74,0:21:11.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誒 別這樣 不要在意啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.83,0:21:14.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,倒是對你來說這裡更重要吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.82,0:21:16.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你姐姐的{\rsymbol}…{\r}那什麼{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.92,0:21:24.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今後一段時間{\rsymbol}…{\r}我會盡力做自己的事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.38,0:21:26.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得這意味著什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.35,0:21:33.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在姐姐最後留下照片的地方 我真正戰鬥了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.84,0:21:36.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐的事我將來一定會查
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.49,0:21:38.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,絕不會忘
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.51,0:21:40.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.11,0:21:41.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在先{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.02,0:21:47.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 這樣也挺好
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.01,0:23:39.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(645,500)\bord3\be1\fs60\fad(500,0)}約定
